    <item>
      <title>参议院投票采取措施迫使特朗普结束伊朗战争</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/senate-iran-war-authorization.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在四名共和党支持者的支持下，民主党赢得了投票，提出一项决议，迫使总统结束敌对行动或赢得国会授权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/senate-iran-war-authorization.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 22:03:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普支持肯·帕克斯顿在德克萨斯州参议院决选中对阵约翰·科宁</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/trump-paxton-endorsement-cornyn-texas-senate.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管共和党领导人就帕克斯顿的丑闻历史发出警告，但总统还是拥抱了“让美国再次伟大”的忠实拥护者肯·帕克斯顿，而不是参议员约翰·科宁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/trump-paxton-endorsement-cornyn-texas-senate.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 21:57:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党参议员对特朗普对帕克斯顿的支持感到愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/republican-senators-trump-paxton.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统冷落四届现任参议员、德克萨斯州参议员约翰·科宁的消息引起了震惊、愤怒和恐惧，因为共和党可能会这样做。可能会失去席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/republican-senators-trump-paxton.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 21:56:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于通胀担忧加剧，债券收益率创 2007 年以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/business/bond-market-iran-war-inflation.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自全球金融危机爆发以来，30年期美国国债收益率从未如此高。在欧洲和亚洲，收益率也有所上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/business/bond-market-iran-war-inflation.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 21:17:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国税局必须放弃对特朗普及其家人的审计</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/trump-irs-doj-lawsuit-audit.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为司法部赔偿基金协议的一部分，官员们发誓不会追究任何悬而未决的事项，包括涉及特朗普总统纳税申报表的事项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/trump-irs-doj-lawsuit-audit.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 20:17:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在全球动荡之际，特朗普炫耀白宫宴会厅建筑</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/05/19/us/politics/trump-white-house-builder.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统展示了他的宴会厅项目的建设，让人们更深入地了解对他来说重要的事情。]]></description>
